        </li>
        <li>Provide the original proof of purchase (receipt) and a detailed description of the defect.</li>
        <li>Send the product, along with any requested documentation, to the address provided by S&H.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="t-font-bold">7. Legal Rights:</span> This guarantee is provided in addition to the statutory rights
        of the consumer under the Australian consumer law and any other applicable law. The statutory rights of the
        consumer are not affected by this AMG guarantee.
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="t-font-bold">8. Additional Provisions:</span> Any claims under this AMG are subject to Australian
        law and must be made within the 30-year guarantee period.
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="t-font-bold">9. Contact Information:</span> For further information or questions, please contact us
